	<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 mix-blend-soft-light" aria-hidden="true">
			<div class="absolute -top-44 -left-56 h-[820px] w-[820px] rounded-full bg-[color:var(--accent)] opacity-[0.06] blur-3xl"></div>
			<div class="absolute -bottom-52 -right-56 h-[880px] w-[880px] rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 opacity-[0.28] blur-3xl"></div>
		</div>
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10">
		<div class="ui-card rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-7" data-reveal>
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Hizmetler</h1>
		<p class="ui-muted mt-3">
			Aşağıdaki hizmetler şubelere göre listelenir. Randevu alırken doğru şubeyi seçmeniz yeterli.
